Scott Brassey 








ProfessionalsMark Matsko, CFAScott BrasseyJustin Yochum, CFADanielle Bugni, CFAJill Wilson 

 Vice President and Portfolio Managert. 208.343.7556f. 208.343.5639E-mailV-Card Scott’s work experience includes fixed income trading and management, financial derivatives and foreign exchange trading, and portfolio management.  He has worked in the capital markets industry since 1984 and has been with the firm since 1998.
Community Involvement
Scott is a member at Hillcrest Country Club.
Education, Licenses and Certifications
Scott received his degree in Finance from the University of Arizona.
Personal Interests
Scott has been active in his kids’ athletic pursuits and enjoys the great Idaho and Oregon outdoors.



 
 
 
 















