Project Information
Location
Boise, Idaho
Owner/Client
Selway Asset Management


Selway Asset Management
LCA Interiors were asked to provide affordable solutions to upgrade and modernize an existing office suite on the 6th floor oft he Wells Fargo Center.
Replacing heavy wooden blinds with subtle window treatments created privacy while maintaining a feeling of openness at both conference rooms and private offices.
Simple solutions such as brighter wall colors, new flooring and light fixtures breathed new life into this office environment, reflecting the energy of the generational work force occupying this space.

